## Code Quality Assessment for YOLO

### Summary
The codebase has been significantly improved over the past iterations. The recent commits have focused on refactoring the terminal UI into a dedicated `TerminalUI` struct with proper synchronization and state management. The code is now well-structured and maintainable, but there are areas that need improvement in terms of testing coverage and some edge case handling.

